00:00:18.820 --> 00:00:22.480
will demonstrate Tollens'
Test, a chemical test created

00:00:22.480 --> 00:00:27.610
by this man, Bernhard
Tollens, a German chemist born

00:00:27.610 --> 00:00:29.500
in the late 1800s.

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:32.530
So let's watch Dr. Dolhun
perform this demonstration here

00:00:32.530 --> 00:00:34.915
at MIT as part of the
Cambridge Science Festival.

00:00:35.650 --> 00:00:39.010
JOHN DOLHUN: OK, so I'm
going to be careful.

